WEBVTT

00:00.100 --> 00:01.901
Maybe we should just elope.

00:01.968 --> 00:03.235
Good idea.

00:03.303 --> 00:04.703
Over my dead body.

00:04.771 --> 00:06.671
Look, you think
your first wedding was great?

00:06.739 --> 00:08.540
You just wait
until you see ours.

00:08.608 --> 00:10.609
Nice looking little
friend you got there.

00:10.676 --> 00:11.742
Miracle girl?

00:11.810 --> 00:12.878
We'll see about that.

00:12.945 --> 00:15.213
<i>The winner is...
Amy Fleming!</i>

00:15.280 --> 00:16.481
I'm in love with you.

00:16.549 --> 00:17.682
How is that a problem?

00:17.900 --> 00:19.600
Eventually you're gonna
break my heart.

00:19.669 --> 00:21.435
I'm just gonna save us
both the trouble

00:21.503 --> 00:22.937
and break my own heart.

00:23.005 --> 00:24.773
I did propose to Lisa.

00:24.840 --> 00:26.007
You guys just take one
of the most important moments

00:26.075 --> 00:27.007
of my life

00:27.075 --> 00:28.175
and hijack it from me?!

00:28.242 --> 00:30.110
We didn't wanna steal
your thunder...

00:30.178 --> 00:32.079
So no, we're not
getting married.

00:32.147 --> 00:33.213
Oh...

