00:57.504 --> 00:59.805
Jack, pick a card. Any card.

00:59.872 --> 01:00.872
No.

01:00.940 --> 01:02.507
Oh, come on! It's awesome.

01:02.575 --> 01:03.508
I said, no.

01:03.576 --> 01:05.077
Why? Are you scared?

01:05.144 --> 01:08.246
No. I don't care to know
the future.

01:08.314 --> 01:09.848
The here and now's
enough to deal with;

01:09.916 --> 01:13.284
I can barely stand to read
the newspaper these days.

01:13.352 --> 01:15.452
Ty! Pick a card.

01:15.520 --> 01:18.522
<i>Concentrate on what you want
the card to tell you.</i>

01:18.590 --> 01:20.357
It's a ship.

01:20.425 --> 01:22.226
<i>The ship.
Very interesting.</i>

01:22.293 --> 01:23.627
It's all about travelling.

01:23.695 --> 01:25.329
You're supposed to take action
of some sort.

01:25.396 --> 01:27.297
Do something that
you've put off.

01:27.365 --> 01:30.701
Like all the chores
I've been bugging you to do.

01:30.768 --> 01:32.268
<i>It could also have
a negative aspect...</i>

01:32.336 --> 01:33.636
As in a sinking ship.

01:33.704 --> 01:36.005
<i>Oh. Thanks, Mallory.</i>

01:36.941 --> 01:38.608
Lou, pick a card.

01:38.675 --> 01:40.576
Um... hmm.

01:41.511 --> 01:42.645
<i>Good one. Clover.</i>

01:42.713 --> 01:43.847
It means potential happiness.

01:43.914 --> 01:45.148
Great.

01:45.216 --> 01:46.449
But since you picked it
with your left hand -

01:46.516 --> 01:48.450
which is weird since
you're right-handed -

01:48.517 --> 01:52.020
the happiness is clouded by
a big fat misunderstanding.

01:52.088 --> 01:53.688
Great. Okay.

01:53.757 --> 01:55.858
I have to go and meet Peter.

01:55.925 --> 01:58.393
I think I've actually found
our dream home,

01:58.461 --> 02:00.863
<i>and Peter's meeting me there
to look at it.</i>

02:00.930 --> 02:02.830
Hey, uh, can I take
your fancy new truck?

02:02.898 --> 02:05.166
Uh... no.
I'm not quite ready to share it.

02:06.869 --> 02:08.301
Keys are on the table.

02:08.370 --> 02:09.436
Thank you.

02:10.604 --> 02:11.672
Pick one.

02:14.943 --> 02:16.377
This one.

02:16.444 --> 02:17.812
<i>The road card.</i>

02:17.880 --> 02:18.879
That means there's a journey
ahead of you.

02:18.946 --> 02:20.180
How mysterious.

02:20.248 --> 02:22.649
But it could also mean
a fork in the road,

02:22.716 --> 02:24.584
- where you...
- Might have to make some big decision?

02:24.652 --> 02:26.119
How'd you know?

02:26.187 --> 02:27.520
Just a wild guess.

02:31.292 --> 02:33.693
Hey, Ty, check this out.

02:34.628 --> 02:36.262
Maybe Mallory's cards do work.

02:36.329 --> 02:38.697
It's an invitation
to the "Ring of Fire" tour.

02:38.765 --> 02:40.166
No way.

02:40.233 --> 02:42.134
It says I eligible since
I won the last competition.

02:42.202 --> 02:43.969
You're not thinking about
doing that again, are you?

02:44.037 --> 02:45.905
I don't know. Uh...

02:45.972 --> 02:48.607
I mean, the last one was
a pretty intense three days,

02:48.675 --> 02:50.642
a little over-the-top
competitive, but...

02:50.710 --> 02:52.376
Yeah. Like you don't have
a competitive bone

02:52.444 --> 02:53.144
in your body.

02:53.212 --> 02:54.145
Ty... what?

02:54.213 --> 02:55.646
When is it?

02:55.714 --> 02:57.648
It's over the
winter school break.

02:57.716 --> 03:00.451
Look at these cities
it's touring.

03:00.519 --> 03:02.620
Hey, you got the ship card,
right?

03:02.688 --> 03:04.488
And I got the road card.

03:04.556 --> 03:05.690
They're both about travelling.

03:05.757 --> 03:06.691
Maybe this means that
you and I should

03:06.758 --> 03:08.758
get in that big truck of mine,

03:08.827 --> 03:09.893
go on the tour together.

03:09.961 --> 03:11.394
Yeah, that could be cool.

03:11.462 --> 03:12.896
Are you kidding?!
This would be amazing!

03:27.544 --> 03:29.145
What do you think?

03:29.213 --> 03:32.081
Construction'll be finished
in May,

03:32.149 --> 03:34.183
but the plans
are still wide open.

03:34.251 --> 03:35.985
We could design
a fabulous kitchen,

03:36.053 --> 03:37.653
maybe an indoor gym...

03:37.721 --> 03:38.821
What do you think?

03:38.888 --> 03:42.157
I think I got something
to tell ya.

03:42.225 --> 03:43.992
You know all the groundwork
I've been laying in Dubai

03:44.060 --> 03:45.160
the last few months, right?

03:45.228 --> 03:46.627
Yeah.

03:46.695 --> 03:48.930
You're not gonna believe this,
it's finally paid off.

03:48.998 --> 03:51.632
My company has an offer
to merge

03:51.700 --> 03:53.835
with an oil company there.
I mean, a big one.

03:53.903 --> 03:55.369
In Dubai.

03:55.436 --> 03:56.937
- No!    - Yeah, it's like the
chance in a lifetime, right?

03:57.005 --> 03:59.473
That's amazing! Oh my God!

03:59.540 --> 04:01.775
I'm so proud of you!

04:03.245 --> 04:04.378
So, now what?

04:04.445 --> 04:06.247
So now, uh, I gotta take
the next step,

04:06.314 --> 04:09.283
and I wanna move forward
with it right away,

04:09.351 --> 04:11.150
and I want you to come with me.

04:11.218 --> 04:13.953
To Dubai? Are you kidding?

04:14.021 --> 04:15.721
As my wife.

04:15.789 --> 04:17.023
As your wife?

04:17.091 --> 04:19.591
But we're not getting married
until...

04:19.659 --> 04:21.094
Like it's months away.

04:21.161 --> 04:23.596
Well, I just think we have
to move that up a little bit.

04:23.663 --> 04:25.064
Uh, to when?

04:25.132 --> 04:27.699
Mm, I don't know... Now?

04:29.835 --> 04:31.435
♪

04:37.710 --> 04:39.310
♪

04:45.183 --> 04:47.584
♪ And at the break of day ♪

04:47.652 --> 04:51.422
♪ you sank into your dream, ♪

04:52.357 --> 04:53.657
♪ you dreamer ♪

04:53.725 --> 04:56.360
♪ Oh, oh, oh... ♪

04:56.428 --> 04:58.429
♪ You dreamer, ♪

05:00.564 --> 05:05.568
♪ you dreamer. ♪

05:06.564 --> 05:09.568
